     windowMs: parseInt(process.env.USER_RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS) || 60 * 1000,
     maxRequests: parseInt(process.env.USER_RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS) || 5,
     message: "Please wait a moment before asking another question"
   };
   ```

5. Ensure the user-based rate limiting works in conjunction with the existing IP-based rate limiting middleware.
